## Detailed Comparison Matrix

| Feature | Databricks | AWS Native | Winner |
|---------|-----------|------------|--------|
| **Compute** | Unified Spark + Photon (10-50x faster) | EMR (manual) or Glue (limited) | 🏆 Databricks |
| **Storage** | Delta Lake (ACID, time travel, built-in) | Parquet (manual) or Iceberg (setup) | 🏆 Databricks |
| **SQL** | Databricks SQL + Photon (fast, unified) | Redshift (separate) or Athena (slow) | 🏆 Databricks |
| **Orchestration** | Workflows (integrated, simple) | Step Functions (complex) or MWAA (setup) | 🏆 Databricks |
| **Governance** | Unity Catalog (advanced, multi-cloud) | Lake Formation (AWS-only, basic) | 🏆 Databricks |
| **ML** | Databricks ML + MLflow (integrated) | SageMaker (separate, complex) | 🏆 Databricks |
| **Cost (Small)** | $150-300/month | $100-200/month | 🏆 AWS |
| **Cost (Large)** | $5K-20K/month (optimized) | $8K-30K/month | 🏆 Databricks |
| **Setup Time** | 5 minutes | 2-4 weeks | 🏆 Databricks |
| **Learning Curve** | Moderate | Steep (many services) | 🏆 Databricks |
| **Flexibility** | Opinionated (best practices) | High (DIY everything) | 🏆 AWS |
| **Multi-Cloud** | AWS, Azure, GCP | AWS only | 🏆 Databricks |

