## Summary

| Aspect | Databricks | AWS Native |
|--------|-----------|------------|
| **Best For** | Unified lakehouse, fast start | Custom solutions, AWS experts |
| **Performance** | 10-50x faster (Photon) | Standard Spark/Presto |
| **Complexity** | Low (1 platform) | High (10+ services) |
| **Cost** | Medium-High | Low-Medium |
| **Flexibility** | Opinionated | Highly flexible |
| **Multi-Cloud** | ✅ Yes | ❌ AWS-only |
| **Time-to-Value** | Days | Weeks-Months |

**Bottom Line**: Databricks for productivity and advanced features, AWS Native for maximum control and cost optimization at small scale.
